&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Clinical Specialist Physiotherapist - Trauma &amp; Related Services &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Band 8a - 1.0 WTE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Trauma &amp; Related Services, in Collaboration with the MSK physiotherapy service at Leeds Teaching Hospitals, are looking to employ a Clinical Specialist Physiotherapist to provide extended scope physiotherapy expertise within the outpatient orthopaedic department at LGI.This post will focus onthe development of the virtual fracture clinic resources. In addition, the post holder will provide specialised assessment, diagnostic review and interventions as appropriate to all patients with fractures. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful applicant must be able to demonstrate significant post-graduate clinical experience, qualifications and personal directed learning within the specialist field of orthopaedic fractures and minor injuries. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;This post offers opportunities for both professional and personal development. We seek those who are interested in service development, education, audit and research. We are dedicated to extending the boundaries of healthcare and allowing you to expand the knowledge in your specialism for the benefit of our patients and the profession.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Above all, we need Physiotherapists with a “can do” attitude who will deliver quality services with compassion.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Interested candidates are invited to discuss this post with:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mr Sam Vollans (Consultant Upper Limb Surgeon) fracture clinic lead sam.vollans@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lorna Williams, Physiotherapy Clinical Manager – MSK and WH Services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Tel: 0113 206 6820, Email: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;lorna.williams@nhs.net&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ben Grange, Service Manager Trauma and Related Services Tel: 0113 39 28723, b.grange@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
